snippet.title: Most UNIQUE and UNEXPECTED CAT & DOG moments! So FUNNY you'll DIE LAUGHING!
snippet.description:
The best and funniest moments with cats and dogs! You will laugh so hard! Look how all these cats & dogs play, make ridiculous sound, behave, annoy each other,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our video, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
